## Game Data (CC BY-SA 4.0)

Game data in `data/machines.json` and `js/data.js` (machine stats, ore values,
gem values, equipment costs, and game mechanics) is derived from the
Ultimate Mining Tycoon Wiki (https://umt.miraheze.org) and is licensed under
the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International License.

You are free to:
- Share: copy and redistribute the data in any medium or format
- Adapt: remix, transform, and build upon the data for any purpose

Under the following terms:
- Attribution: You must give appropriate credit to the UMT Wiki and its
  contributors, provide a link to the license, and indicate if changes were made.
- ShareAlike: If you remix, transform, or build upon the data, you must
  distribute your contributions under the same license.

Full license text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

